<div class="founder-pg">

  <!-- ── HERO — name prominent like Maiweskin ── -->
  <div class="fpg-hero">
    <div class="fpg-hero-eyebrow-wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | default: 'founder' }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fpg-hero-name-wrap">
      <h1 class="fpg-founder-name-headline">Vanessa<br>Freitas</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── FOUNDER PORTRAIT + INTRO ── -->
  <div class="fpg-portrait-section">

    <div class="fpg-portrait-wrap">
      {%- if section.settings.portrait != blank -%}
        <img src="{{ section.settings.portrait | image_url: width: 900 }}" alt="{{ section.settings.founder_name | default: 'Founder' }}" class="fpg-portrait">
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="fpg-portrait fpg-portrait--placeholder"></div>
      {%- endif -%}
      <div class="fpg-portrait-caption">
        <span class="fpg-portrait-name">{{ section.settings.founder_name | default: 'Vanessa Freitas' }}</span>
        <span class="fpg-portrait-location">{{ section.settings.founder_location | default: 'Brussels, Belgium' }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fpg-intro-text">
      <div class="fpg-pull-quote">
        <p>{{ section.settings.pull_quote | default: '"I want to create for me and for those who come after me, a life with better opportunities."' }}</p>
      </div>
      <p class="fpg-intro-body">{{ section.settings.intro_body | default: 'ARCHETYPE was not born in a laboratory. It was born in a kitchen in Brussels, from late nights, a crying baby, botanical research, and an unshakeable belief that women deserve more from their haircare.' }}</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ── STORY CHAPTERS ── -->
  <div class="fpg-story">

    <!-- Chapter 1: Origins -->
    <div class="fpg-chapter">
      <div class="fpg-chapter-num">01</div>
      <div class="fpg-chapter-content">
        <h2 class="fpg-chapter-title">{{ section.settings.ch1_title | default: 'From the bakery to Brussels.' }}</h2>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch1_p1 | default: 'Born and raised with limited opportunities, she learned early the value of resilience. From her first job at a local bakery at 13, to selling Avon cosmetics at 16 door-to-door in her neighbourhood, to earning a 100% scholarship at a private university in São Paulo at 18 — every step was forged through determination.' }}</p>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch1_p2 | default: 'The biggest leap came when she left everything behind and moved to Belgium. Without speaking the language, she did it all: cleaning houses, babysitting, raising her daughter Aurora alone. It was Aurora who unknowingly sparked everything.' }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Chapter 2: Discovery -->
    <div class="fpg-chapter fpg-chapter--alt">
      <div class="fpg-chapter-num">02</div>
      <div class="fpg-chapter-content">
        <h2 class="fpg-chapter-title">{{ section.settings.ch2_title | default: 'A daughter, a question, and essential oils.' }}</h2>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch2_p1 | default: 'Aurora was an active baby — never sleeping more than two hours at a stretch. Desperate for answers, she turned to natural remedies. Aromatherapy became her obsession. Essential oils transformed their nights. And as she shared her journey online, something unexpected happened: hundreds of women around the world began asking the same question.' }}</p>
        <blockquote class="fpg-chapter-quote">
          <p>"By chance, don't you also have any personalized remedies to recover my hair's health?"</p>
        </blockquote>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch2_p2 | default: 'They all shared similar issues — unhealthy scalp microbiome, hair loss, thin hair in need of moisture — caused by different factors: stress, hormones, nutrition. The same problems. The same gap in the market.' }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Chapter 3: The Kitchen Lab -->
    <div class="fpg-chapter">
      <div class="fpg-chapter-num">03</div>
      <div class="fpg-chapter-content">
        <h2 class="fpg-chapter-title">{{ section.settings.ch3_title | default: 'A kitchen becomes a cosmetics lab.' }}</h2>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch3_p1 | default: 'She began creating a cream base and shampoo base that any woman could use — then customize with targeted boosters for their specific needs. A fortifying booster. A deep moisture one. A protein-rich formula. The concept was simple and radical: one base, infinite formulas.' }}</p>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch3_p2 | default: 'Between 2022 and 2023 she hosted four cosmetics workshops. In January 2024, she launched an online platform with cosmetics courses. Her client base grew so fast her kitchen transformed into a full-fledged cosmetics lab. She took botanical formulation courses. She certified her formulations to meet every safety standard.' }}</p>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch3_p3 | default: 'After three years of validating the idea, it was time to share it with the world.' }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Chapter 4: ARCHETYPE -->
    <div class="fpg-chapter fpg-chapter--alt fpg-chapter--last">
      <div class="fpg-chapter-num">04</div>
      <div class="fpg-chapter-content">
        <h2 class="fpg-chapter-title">{{ section.settings.ch4_title | default: 'ARCHETYPE is born.' }}</h2>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch4_p1 | default: 'ARCHETYPE is the sum of every experience — every resilient act, every late night, every woman who asked for something better. It is a brand built on the belief that personalized, natural haircare should be accessible to every woman, regardless of hair type, background, or budget.' }}</p>
        <p>{{ section.settings.ch4_p2 | default: 'All of her life experiences are part of her professional journey, because they have built who she is today: a fierce woman who wants to conquer the life she deserves — and help other women do the same.' }}</p>
        <div class="fpg-chapter-cta">
          <a href="{{ section.settings.cta1_url | default: '/pages/our-story' }}" class="btn-dark">{{ section.settings.cta1_label | default: 'Read our story' }}</a>
          <a href="{{ section.settings.cta2_url | default: '/collections/all' }}" class="fpg-link-cta">{{ section.settings.cta2_label | default: 'Explore the collection →' }}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ── CLOSING QUOTE ── -->
  <div class="fpg-closing">
    <div class="fpg-closing-inner">
      <p class="fpg-closing-quote">{{ section.settings.closing_quote | default: '"All of my life experiences are part of my professional journey, because they have built who I am today."' }}</p>
      {%- if section.settings.founder_name != blank -%}
        <p class="fpg-closing-name">— {{ section.settings.founder_name }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}
      <p class="fpg-closing-brand">Founder, ARCHETYPE</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

